commit.message: fix bitfield, export DataGetter, fix datatypes tests, fix benchmark

add simple parser example, and fix bug in serializer :
* it is possible we already got more data when getting in the moreData promise, so call the callback right now if that's the case
* the callback of _transform needs to be called when the chunk has been processed, not when an object has been produced, call that callback when the data getter emits 'needMoreData'. That event gets emitted in moreData()
fix the benchmark (needed because of the small buffers production)
simplify the write interface by letting the user provide his own buffer
size is not needed in the benchmark

concat the buffers in the serializer

useful for nmp, maybe this should be an option of the serializer, since it's not needed for other protocols

reorganize files, cleanup parsePacketBuffer and createPacketBuffer

still testing on dependents projects, and the doc isn't updated for this change yet
fix option and allow count==-1 for restBuffer
add back some error handling and add a test for varint
